[SPEAKER_01] Nekad sam bio i umoran da molit nekog da ponovi.

318
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ono, odlumiš da si razumio.

319
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,000
