473
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prva obskrba protezom, prihvat te odljede,

474
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] je bilo jako teško.

475
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Paralelno sam odlazio na psihološka savjetovanja

476
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i podršku.

477
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odlazio sam na razgovor kod psihologinje

478
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] koja me pokušala motivirati za svaki dan

479
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] i radila te psihologijska testiranja.

480
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovako što se ja više odlazio,

481
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidio sam da je imao sve manje ideja

482
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako više da me motivira.

483
00:38:58,000 --> 00:39:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno su bile kompleksne ozljede

484
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nekom ko ne vidi, ne čuje,

485
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne može samo sada hodati,

486
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] i malo toga može ostalo da ga može umotivirati

487
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ponuditi mu optimizam

488
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ono, vjerujem da će biti dobro.

489
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujem da će biti dobro,

490
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] samo je teško posložiti sve te emocije

491
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje dolaze u jednu,

492
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] ono koje navale u jednu trenutku,

493
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] se te osjećaja i zbog sami ozljede koje nastaju.

494
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se je nakon tog jednog dugog razbora

495
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada psihologin je izašavanka

496
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] i pita majka kako je bilo.

497
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ja govorim:

498
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ma žena ima sto problema".

499
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi ja rekao:

500
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Vidim da sve teže,

501
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] postoji pitanje,

502
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa 23 sekundi šutnja,

503
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ja govorim:

504
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Lako je za mene, ja ću se nekako staći,

505
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] mami, kako ste vi meni?"

506
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo mi tu pričali o problemu,

507
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] da smo mi zamijenili te uloge,

508
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] da mi je to bila fora,

509
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda se odlazio tamo

510
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] i sad te nalaze sam sam,

511
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim:

512
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Rekao sam jučer da ne imam nesanicu,

513
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne imam u noću,

514
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] baš nisam dobro spavao,

515
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] idem opet malo."

516
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je bilo jako meni to zanimljivo,

517
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve kroz umore za zanci.

518
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila meni podrška u tim trenucima,

519
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ovako imao sam dobar odnos

520
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] i s osobljom i sa doktorcem gore,

521
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada je bila u Toplicama

522
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] i sestrama.

523
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio to jedan tim koji je bio stalno oko mene,

524
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] pružava podršku, tako da,

525
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] kroz tu rehabilitaciju

526
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kroz to druženje sa prijateljima

527
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje sam gore upoznao.

528
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Upoznao sam puno mladih ljudi koji stradali

529
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] u prometnim nezgodanama,

530
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] u skokove, u vodu na glavu,

531
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] upadao iz visine.

532
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Većina su bile spinalne ozljede,

533
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] ozljede kralježnice.

534
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

535
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] oni su isto prolazili kroz težak period života,

536
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad su 18 godina.

537
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Većina su to bili mladi momce od 18 do 30 godina.

538
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su svjesni da oporavak će trati jako dugo

539
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da većina njih, ako je došla do prilama

540
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] ilo većeg štećenja ledne moždine da se nikad ne oporavio.

541
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam nekako imao potrebu njih motivirati.

542
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno,

543
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] bio sam dvi godine gore i onda mi se javila ideja.

544
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ono, kad god neko dođe novi,

545
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] sjetim se kako sam sijao svjeća.

546
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Totalna, što kaže, u baljani sam bio puno toga upitnika nad glavom,

547
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] puno neizvjesnih stvari.

548
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne zna što te čeka.

549
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu smo bili ja i majka i sve medicijsko osoblje koje radi svoj posao,

550
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje te pruža.

551
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se uzdizao kroz molitu vjeru i taj neki optimizam koji je bio nadrealan.

552
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam da je dolazio s neba tim najgorijim trenucima,

553
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] najtežijim sad da bio nekako duhovnu snagu.

554
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda bi došla bi jednostavno u molitve misla kao:

555
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Oke, ti si u mraku, gdje god poglaš oko sebe je mrak,

556
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ti danas zanese nekom svjetlo kao u životu u dan, u veselega."

557
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda bi tako odao po oddjelu, odajem na recepciju,

558
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer došak o novi.

559
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] To mi kaže sto, tri soba.

560
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] O tu i tu, tako je ta ozljeda.

561
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda tamo odajem i ono predstavim se čisto malo kroz humor i kroz šalu.

562
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam imao neke spontane zaparkancije.

563
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono ko je bio lakše ozljede,

564
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] ko je imao teže ozljede te kralježnice,

565
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi znao zaparkat malo više.

566
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj deč ko je odbijao rate se vježbe,

567
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] odbijao surađivati,

568
00:42:58,000 --> 00:43:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi mene ovaj fizioterapeut pa u sada kaže:

569
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ovaj neće još ko, neće ovaj da vježba,

570
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] daj toga mene, da odem tamo."

571
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam došao ovdje.

572
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam tijel surađivati.

573
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidiš kao se mene ruku na panj.

574
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam svijetno shvatio da moram vježbat.

575
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja govorio o terapeuciji,

576
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] ajde ozljede dalje.

577
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] odbijao na facu.

578
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on govorno pitao kako je ovaj ljudi naš pripase.

579
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi je bilo jasno.

580
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo se posli skompali i družili.

581
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I skužili svi brzo da se java iza frakanta.

582
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vodio od crnih humor,

583
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali draba zazancija na naši računi.

584
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedne druge smo bodrili u tim teškim trenutcima.

585
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno trebaš motivira ljuda da daju svoj maksimum.

586
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] onako zavruće rane da se najviše kod takvih pozljeda može napraviti napredova.

587
00:43:55,000 --> 00:44:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nekako sam se trudio biti nasmijan i pozitivan.

588
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi ljudi koji su mi dolazi u posjetu stvarno je bio veliki broj ljudi koji mi dolazi u posjetu.

589
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bi li podruška prijatelji, rodina, obitelja, osoblje, medicinsko s kojima sam se prijateljio.

590
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako se ja tu svu nekakvu energiju.

591
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što sam ja dobio da bi se dobro osjeća.

592
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećaj mi ruku korisnim da nekog to raspoložiš.

593
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je to bilo drago da mogu dobar dan reći na hodniku.

594
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] U nekoj bake u Ljepša dan ili Zezacena.

595
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Toplicama sam baš nekako doživio taj duhovni rast.

596
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Shvatio sam kako sam shvatio da život više nikad neće biti isti.

597
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan sam sve više pridavao sebe dragom Bogu.

598
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da On upravi svaki novi dan.

599
00:44:57,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja vjerujem da je tu najveći moj rast bio u tom procesu rehabilitata.

600
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da evo i onda ste pitali.

601
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako se razvila ta želja za psihologijom.

602
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je trebalo pisaći studij.

603
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebala mi je matura.

604
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Više razne engleskog i psihologija, izborni predmet.

605
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda zove rodbirno, zove prijatelje da mi čitaju primjere prijašnji matura.

606
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebala to spremati.

607
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj engleski malo.

608
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu se imao slabiju podlogu iz osnovne škole.

609
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda me to pratilo kroz cijelo obrazovanje.

610
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek se imao nekako fobiju tog engleskog.

611
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pripremao se za tu maturu, položio to.

612
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da su mi bili podrška ubijitelj prijatelji.

613
00:45:48,000 --> 00:45:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nakon što sam položio, zakasnije sam prijavljeno.

614
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tijel sam u Zagrebi na katoličko...

615
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatski katolički.

616
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

617
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] To sam tijel na fakultet.

618
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da sam zakasnijel jer su mi nešto.

619
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da nisam uplatio.

620
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pošto polažem maturu drugi put nisam neko uplatnicu uplatio.

621
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Makli su me sa popse.

622
00:46:13,000 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ulazim tam u ran rezultate.

623
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, nigde niste prijavljeni.

624
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je odjavljeno.

625
00:46:18,000 --> 00:46:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prošle rokovi.

626
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije još bila matura.

627
00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možete mi nekako staviti.

628
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, platiš sve kogo treba.

629
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno nismo znali da treba platiti.

630
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo pratili te obavijesti.

631
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Majka slabije se snalazila na internetu.

632
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ja nisam bio mogućnosti za to poplaćenje.

633
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako smo to sanirali, ostalo jedino slobodno zadar.

634
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja razmišljam more, slunce.

635
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem bio godina dana na obuci, na školovanju u Zagrebu.

636
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, tmurno, uvijek išemo.

637
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije noš Zadar taj.

638
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo u Zagrebu.

639
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nisam bio u Zagrebu.

640
00:46:57,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prolazio jesan, ali nisam nikad se zaustavljal.

641
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] i uopći ima predožbu kako grad izgledan

642
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kako će to sve izgledat.

643
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Potpuno slijep.

644
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam ima neku pozitivni taj ljudi,

645
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] optimizam koji me država to sve to vrijeme,

646
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve to godina kroz rehabilitaciju.

647
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo u Zagrebu i onda je tu majka.

648
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Majka mi je rekla šta god ti odlučiš,

649
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam uz tebe.

650
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je bitno da ti pronađeš neki svoj put

651
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je stvarno žrtvala tu sve svoje vrijeme.

652
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Praktički taj period i u bolnici,

653
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] dok je bila sa mnou u Dubravi i u Toplicama,

654
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] odrekla se svog života da bi bila meni podrška.

655
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Potrebno je bila 24 sat na pomoć.

656
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno to država nima načina da osigura

657
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] i majka je bila tu koja je bila uz mene.

658
00:47:55,000 --> 00:48:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer da je bilo drugačije bio bi samo u bolničkoj sobi,

659
